{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2357,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252922,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":256174,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":274230,"text":"Thank you!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275476,"text":"(Applause continues)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280203,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":282616,"text":"Like the speaker before me --\nI am a TED virgin, I guess."},{"time":287322,"text":"I'm also the first time here, and ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290278,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291423,"text":"I don't know what to say!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":292708,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":296165,"text":"I'm really happy\nthat Mr. Anderson invited me."},{"time":299000,"text":"I'm really grateful that I get a chance\nto play for everyone."},{"time":302523,"text":"And the song that I just played\nwas by Josef Hofmann."},{"time":305818,"text":"It's called \"Kaleidoscope.\""},{"time":307691,"text":"And Hofmann is a Polish pianist\nand composer of the late 19th century,"},{"time":314378,"text":"and he's widely considered\none of the greatest pianists of all time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318173,"text":"I have another piece\nthat I'd like to play for you."},{"time":320729,"text":"It's called \"Abegg Variations,\"\nby Robert Schumann,"},{"time":324796,"text":"a German 19th-century composer."},{"time":328994,"text":"The name \"Abegg\" is actually A-B-E-G-G,"},{"time":333169,"text":"and that's the main theme in the melody."},{"time":335136,"text":"(Plays the notes A, B, E, G and G)"},{"time":339007,"text":"That comes from the last name\nof one of Schumann's female friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343673,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345470,"text":"But he wrote that for his wife."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347597,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":351715,"text":"So actually, if you listen carefully,"},{"time":353565,"text":"there are supposed to be\nfive variations on this Abegg theme."},{"time":356986,"text":"It's written around 1834,"},{"time":359614,"text":"so even though it's old,\nI hope you'll like it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365583,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":774987,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":778312,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":785748,"text":"Now comes the part that I hate."},{"time":790591,"text":"Well, because Mr. Anderson told me"},{"time":793071,"text":"that this session is called\n\"Sync and Flow,\""},{"time":795972,"text":"I was wondering, \"What do I know\nthat these geniuses don't?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":798993,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800184,"text":"So, I'll talk about musical composition,"},{"time":802333,"text":"even though I don't know where to start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805679,"text":"How do I compose?"},{"time":807544,"text":"I think Yamaha does a really good job\nof teaching us how to compose."},{"time":811452,"text":"What I do first is, I make a lot\nof little musical ideas"},{"time":815163,"text":"you can just improvise\nhere at the piano --"},{"time":817378,"text":"and I choose one of those\nto become my main theme, my main melody,"},{"time":821119,"text":"like the Abegg that you just heard."},{"time":823300,"text":"And once I choose my main theme,\nI have to decide:"},{"time":826826,"text":"Out of all the styles in music,\nwhat kind of style do I want?"},{"time":830628,"text":"And this year,\nI composed a Romantic style."},{"time":833568,"text":"So for inspiration,\nI listened to Liszt and Tchaikovsky"},{"time":837469,"text":"and all the great Romantic composers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839960,"text":"Next, I make the structure\nof the entire piece with my teachers."},{"time":845443,"text":"They help me plan out the whole piece."},{"time":847412,"text":"And then the hard part\nis filling it in with musical ideas,"},{"time":851138,"text":"because then you have to think."}]},{"cues":[{"time":853136,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":854933,"text":"And then, when the piece\ntakes somewhat of a solified form --"},{"time":858436,"text":"solidified, excuse me -- solidified form,"},{"time":860682,"text":"you're supposed to actually\npolish the piece, polish the details,"},{"time":865732,"text":"and then polish the overall\nperformance of the composition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":869843,"text":"And another thing\nthat I enjoy doing is drawing."},{"time":872912,"text":"Drawing, because I like to draw,\nyou know, Japanese anime art."},{"time":876420,"text":"I think that's a craze\namong teens right now."},{"time":879385,"text":"And once I realized it,"},{"time":881061,"text":"there's a parallel between creating\nmusic and creating art,"},{"time":885081,"text":"because for your motive, or your\nlittle initial idea for your drawing,"},{"time":890215,"text":"it's your character -- you want\nto decide who you want to draw,"},{"time":893207,"text":"or if you want to draw\nan original character."},{"time":895387,"text":"And then you want to decide:\nHow are you going to draw the character?"},{"time":898908,"text":"Like, am I going to use one page?\nAm I going to draw it on the computer?"},{"time":902344,"text":"Am I going to use a two-page spread\nlike a comic book?"},{"time":905544,"text":"For a more grandiose effect, I guess."},{"time":908131,"text":"And then you have to do\nthe initial sketch of the character,"},{"time":911302,"text":"which is like your structure of a piece,"},{"time":913364,"text":"and then you add pen and pencil,\nand whatever details that you need --"},{"time":917148,"text":"that's polishing the drawing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919025,"text":"And another thing that both of these\nhave in common is your state of mind,"},{"time":922771,"text":"because I know I'm one of those teenagers\nthat are really easily distracted."},{"time":927781,"text":"So if I'm trying to do homework\nand I don't feel like it,"},{"time":932820,"text":"I'll try to draw or,\nyou know, waste my time."},{"time":935999,"text":"And then what happens is,\nsometimes I absolutely can't draw"},{"time":938801,"text":"or I can't compose at all,"},{"time":940786,"text":"and then it's like\nthere's too much on your mind."},{"time":943116,"text":"You can't focus\non what you're supposed to do."},{"time":945517,"text":"And sometimes, if you manage to use\nyour time wisely and work on it,"},{"time":950842,"text":"you'll get something out of it,\nbut it doesn't come naturally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954486,"text":"What happens is,\nif something magical happens,"},{"time":956994,"text":"if something natural happens to you,"},{"time":959622,"text":"you're able to produce\nall this beautiful stuff instantly,"},{"time":963265,"text":"and then that's what I consider \"flow,\""},{"time":965417,"text":"because that's when everything clicks\nand you're able to do anything."},{"time":969409,"text":"You feel like you're on top of your game\nand you can do anything you want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":973194,"text":"I'm not going to play\nmy own composition today because,"},{"time":976439,"text":"although I did finish it,\nit's way too long."},{"time":980050,"text":"Instead, I'd like to try something\ncalled \"improvisation.\""},{"time":983262,"text":"I have here seven note cards,"},{"time":985507,"text":"one with each note\nof the musical alphabet."},{"time":988714,"text":"And I'd like someone to come up here\nand choose five --"},{"time":992621,"text":"anyone to come up here and choose five --"},{"time":994633,"text":"and then I can make it\ninto some sort of melody,"},{"time":997369,"text":"and I'll improvise it."},{"time":999711,"text":"Wow. A volunteer, yay!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002866,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1004364,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1007514,"text":"Jennifer Lin: Nice to meet you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009633,"text":"Goldie Hawn: Thank you. Choose five?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012644,"text":"JL: Yes, five cards. Any five cards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014730,"text":"GH: OK, one.\nJL: OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1017185,"text":"GH: Two.\nJL: Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020025,"text":"GH: Three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1023009,"text":"GH: Oh, D and F -- too familiar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1025532,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1030165,"text":"JL: One more.\nGH: OK. \"E\" for \"effort.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1033525,"text":"JL: Would you mind reading them out\nin the order that you chose them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1036820,"text":"GH: OK -- C, G, B, A and E."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1043135,"text":"JL: Thank you very much!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1044313,"text":"GH: You're welcome. And what about these?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046313,"text":"JL: I won't use them. Thank you!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1050204,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1057152,"text":"Now, she chose C, G, B, A, E."},{"time":1060554,"text":"I'm going to try to put that\nin some sort of order."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1062998,"text":"(Plays notes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1068606,"text":"OK, that's nice."},{"time":1071036,"text":"So, I'm going to have a moment to think,"},{"time":1072997,"text":"and I'll try to make something out of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1080134,"text":"(Plays the five notes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1091044,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1287201,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1289226,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1296028,"text":"The next song, or the encore\nthat I'm going to play"},{"time":1298616,"text":"is called \"Bumble Boogie,\" by Jack Fina."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1302979,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1307689,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1419521,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1421546,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}